                    <h5 class="d-flex is-justify-content-space-between">
                      Does ERA support the no-kill movement?
                    </h5>
                    <div class="carrot"></div>
                  </header>
                  <div class="accord-content text-med-grey double-spaced">
                    <p>
                      While the no-kill movement has brought attention to the importance of saving lives, it has also contributed to
                      the animal welfare crisis by creating a culture of hoarding and a lack of accountability.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      We believe that the no-kill movement has ultimately done more harm than good, and that our focus should be on improving the
                      lives of animals in rescues and shelters rather than on saving every life at all costs.  We believe that euthanasia
                      is a necessary evil, and that sometimes it is the most humane option for an animal that is suffering mentally or physically.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </section>
