                    </h5>
                    <div class="carrot"></div>
                  </header>
                  <div class="accord-content text-med-grey double-spaced">
                    <p>
                      We believe that abortive spays are a necessary step in reducing the number of animals in shelters and rescues.
                      While we understand that this is a controversial topic, we believe that it is a more humane option than
                      allowing an animal to be born into a world that is overpopulated with animals that are already in
                      need of homes. We believe that the resources put towards birthing litters, vaccinating and deworming them,
                      and getting them adopted out could be better spent on animals that are already here and in need of care.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </section>
